      <title>西班牙首相将 BBVA 收购萨瓦德尔银行的事宜提交监管机构审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/spain-prime-minister-defers-to-watchdog-on-bbva-s-sabadell-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯并未对西班牙对外银行 (BBVA SA) 收购萨瓦德尔银行 (Banco Sabadell SA) 的提议做出评判，尽管西班牙政府此前曾对这项银行业交易表示强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/spain-prime-minister-defers-to-watchdog-on-bbva-s-sabadell-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 09:41:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放宽长期资金规则以提振股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/china-eases-rules-for-long-term-funds-to-support-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国推出了一揽子措施稳定股市，其中包括计划增加养老金对国内上市公司的投资额度，以应对唐纳德·特朗普第二任总统任期内的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/china-eases-rules-for-long-term-funds-to-support-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 09:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
